text.data-name: Started a CleanUp at Palm Beach, FL

1. Map Interactive map shows users current location and CleanUps nearby. Different types of CleanUps are marked with different styles, namely reported beach, recruiting CleanUps and CleanUps waiting for approval.

tspan.tspan: Interactive map shows users current location and
CleanUps nearby. Different types of CleanUps are
marked with different styles, namely reported
beach, recruiting CleanUps and CleanUps waiting
for approval.

text.data-name: 1. Message Screen with 2 sections, Notification box shows Notifications rolling. Chats shows the chat with individual chats and group chats.

tspan.tspan: Screen with 2 sections, Notification box shows
Notifications rolling. Chats shows the chat with
individual chats and group chats.

text.data-name: 1. Dashboard Dashboard contains the detail information of the CleanUp with 6 panels: Members, Assignment, Equipment, Group Chat, Photos and Reports.

tspan.tspan: Dashboard contains the detail information of the
CleanUp with 6 panels: Members, Assignment,
Equipment, Group Chat, Photos and Reports.

text.data-name: 1.User Profile shows information about user, following, followers, contribution to the Ocean Blue Project, and personal info. Upcoming CleanUp section will show up when user has a ongoing CleanUp, then follows the posts from the user.

tspan.tspan: shows information about user, following, followers,
contribution to the Ocean Blue Project, and
personal info. Upcoming CleanUp section will show
up when user has a ongoing CleanUp, then follows
the posts from the user.

text.data-name: 1. Daily Ocean Knowledge Daily feeds of facts and knowledges about ocean, plastic pollution , etc. Current state of global oceanic pollution research with data visualization.

tspan.tspan: Daily feeds of facts and knowledges about ocean,
plastic pollution , etc.
Current state of global oceanic pollution research
with data visualization.

text.data-name: 1. Social Social feeds from user’s following list, recruitment info from ongoing CleanUp allowing user to browse share and join.

tspan.tspan: Social feeds from user’s following list, recruitment
info from ongoing CleanUp allowing user to browse
share and join.

text.data-name: 4. Join a CleanUp When user taps on a CleanUp recruiting members, a popup shows the detail of the CleanUp and the Join button.

tspan.tspan: When user taps on a CleanUp recruiting members,
a popup shows the detail of the CleanUp and the
Join button.

text.data-name: 3. Create CleanUp User can tap on reported beach on the map, the popup shows the detail of the current state of beach by description and photos.

tspan.tspan: User can tap on reported beach on the map, the
popup shows the detail of the current state of
beach by description and photos.

text.data-name: 2. My CleanUp status When user has a CleanUp waiting for approval, approved, ongoing CleanUp, this section will appear and show the progress.

tspan.tspan: When user has a CleanUp waiting for approval,
approved, ongoing CleanUp, this section will
appear and show the progress.

text.data-name: 2. Members Member Popup shows the current members of the group.

tspan.tspan: Member Popup shows the current members of the
group.

text.data-name: 2. Contribution shows the contribution user has made for the Ocean Blue Project and ranking among all the global users.

tspan.tspan: shows the contribution user has made for the
Ocean Blue Project and ranking among all the
global users.

text.data-name: 2. Feed Detail Featured articles pushed daily by Ocean Blue Project Organization.

tspan.tspan: Featured articles pushed daily by Ocean Blue
Project Organization.

text.data-name: 2. Articles User can post/repost articles, like and bookmark them. Articles that are liked or bookmarked will be saved into personal section.

tspan.tspan: User can post/repost articles, like and bookmark
them. Articles that are liked or bookmarked will be
saved into personal section.

text.data-name: 3. My CleanUp status Change of status from waiting for approval to approved.

tspan.tspan: Change of status from waiting for approval to
approved.

text.data-name: 3. Assignment Assignment Popup shows the sections of the target beach and the number of assigned cleaners.

tspan.tspan: Assignment Popup shows the sections of the
target beach and the number of assigned cleaners.

text.data-name: 3. Join a CleanUp Join a CleanUp on network feeds, user can see the location, dates, estimated duration and brief descriptions about the CleanUp, and the current members, users contacts will be put in the front.

tspan.tspan: Join a CleanUp on network feeds, user can see the
location, dates, estimated duration and brief
descriptions about the CleanUp, and the current
members, users contacts will be put in the front.

text.data-name: 4. Join a CleanUp A popup window for user’s contact info and ask user to check the agreement. after joining, user will be led to Dashboard to finish the rest of action.

tspan.tspan: A popup window for user’s contact info and ask
user to check the agreement. after joining, user will
be led to Dashboard to finish the rest of action.

text.data-name: 4. Promote Your CleanUp When user has a CleanUp recruiting members, or a CleanUp still waiting for approval, the user can share this to the CleanUp network or other Social Media Platforms.

tspan.tspan: When user has a CleanUp recruiting members, or a
CleanUp still waiting for approval, the user can
share this to the CleanUp network or other Social

text.data-name: 4. Assignment When a section is clicked, shows the current group of selected section. CleanUp owner can assign members to be leading roles.

tspan.tspan: When a section is clicked, shows the current group
of selected section. CleanUp owner can assign
members to be leading roles.

text.data-name: 5. Set reminder for a CleanUp When user taps on a CleanUp that is waiting for approval, user can set a reminder, so that when it is approved, user will get notified in Message section

tspan.tspan: When user taps on a CleanUp that is waiting for
approval, user can set a reminder, so that when it is
approved, user will get notified in Message section

text.data-name: 2. Report Beach User can take photos of a beach that needs to be cleaned, and report the beach. Reported beach will be waiting for other users to create a CleanUp event.

tspan.tspan: User can take photos of a beach that needs to be
cleaned, and report the beach. Reported beach will
be waiting for other users to create a CleanUp
event.

text.data-name: 5. CleanUp approved When user’s CleanUp is approved, the creating step is finished, user can manage CleanUp in the dashboard. The status in Message screen will change to recruiting.

tspan.tspan: When user’s CleanUp is approved, the creating step
is finished, user can manage CleanUp in the
dashboard. The status in Message screen will
change to recruiting.

text.data-name: 5. Equipment Equipment list and progress of current and target number of equipment.

tspan.tspan: Equipment list and progress of current and target
number of equipment.

text.data-name: 6.Create CleanUp step 1 Step 1. User fills up the Starter info, and set the amount of equipments they would need, normally recommended by the app by calculating the size of the group.

tspan.tspan: Step 1. User fills up the Starter info, and set the
amount of equipments they would need, normally
recommended by the app by calculating the size of
the group.

text.data-name: 6. Individual Chats User can talk to other users when mutually followed.

tspan.tspan: User can talk to other users when mutually
followed.

text.data-name: 6. Photos Photos of team cleaning up beaches, group photos, memorable moments.

tspan.tspan: Photos of team cleaning up beaches, group
photos, memorable moments.

text.data-name: 7. Create CleanUp step 2 Step 2. Read the organizer agreement, and send the the application, which will be approved by OBP. User can check application status in Message section. And user’s application will appear on the map, other users can tap and set Rem

tspan.tspan: Step 2. Read the organizer agreement, and send
the the application, which will be approved by OBP.
User can check application status in Message
section. And user’s application will appear on the
map, other users can tap and set Reminder.

text.data-name: 7. Create CleanUp step 2 Step 2. Read the organizer agreement, and send the the application, which will be approved by OBP. User can check application status in Message section. And user’s application will appear on the map, other users can tap and set Rem

tspan.tspan: Step 2. Read the organizer agreement, and send
the the application, which will be approved by OBP.
User can check application status in Message
section. And user’s application will appear on the
map, other users can tap and set Reminder.

text.data-name: 7. Group Chats When user creates or joins a CleanUp, a Group chat is automatically created for members to communicate.

tspan.tspan: When user creates or joins a CleanUp, a Group chat
is automatically created for members to
communicate.

text.data-name: 7. My CleanUp status When user confirms the approval, the status will change to recruiting, where other users can join through map or social network.

tspan.tspan: When user confirms the approval, the status will
change to recruiting, where other users can join
through map or social network.

text.data-name: 7. Reports Reports will be edited by the assigned reporter from each section. Other users can only view the report content but not edit.

tspan.tspan: Reports will be edited by the assigned reporter
from each section. Other users can only view the
report content but not edit.

text.data-name: 8. Reports Assigned reporter can add pictures, title and description of the debris in the section.

tspan.tspan: Assigned reporter can add pictures, title and
description of the debris in the section.
